INGREDIENTS
For filling:
Potato(boiled and peeled, big) - 2 nos
Carrots(chopped) - 2 nos
Green peas - 1/2 cup
Onion(sliced) - 3 nos
Green chiliies(chopped) - 6 nos
Ginger(chopped) - 1 tsp
Turmeric powder - 1/2 tsp
Salt(As reqd) -
For batter:-
Gram flour(Besan/Kadalamaavu) - 1 1/2 cups
Salt(As reqd) -
Water -
Oil for frying -